title: Episode 31: Backstage at the 2016 UW-Green Bay PSI Talks
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: In this last episode of the fall semester, Dr. Ryan Martin talks with the four speakers from the 2016 PSI Talks (blog.uwgb.edu/uwgbpsych/psi-talks/).  Allee Schramm, Olyvia Kuchta, Annie Jones, and Tonya Filz share why the decided to submit a talk, how they are feeling about the event, and what they plan on talking about.
